gc.pmb_library.android.api.interfaces
Interface TagListener

public interface TagListener

The listener interface for receiving tag events. The class that is interested in processing a tag event implements this interface, and the object created with that class is registered with a component using the component's addTagListener method. When the tag event occurs, that object's appropriate method is invoked. This interface must be implemented to receive messages or the Tags for the operations with Tags.(set/get/delete Tags)
